			<img src="/global_images/spacer.gif" height="10" width="1"><br><div class="body_title">Exhibitor Press Conferences and Events<br><img src="/global_images/spacer.gif" height="16" width="1"></div>
			

<div id="2.3.5.5">	
<!-- text for main page -->
From holding press conferences to participating in a conference session panel, International CES exhibitors can connect with the press and analyst communities to tell their story, show their products and demonstrate their expertise. Use a variety of pre-show or on-site services and programs to execute your PR plan. 
