<div class="section_title">CES-TV</div>
Get your message across using TVs on throughout the show locations
<br><br>
With fresh content every day, CES-TV will have reports from the show floor, product reviews, interviews, show news and excerpts from keynotes.  Through CES-TV, attendees can keep abreast of everything happening at CES.
<br><br>
CES-TV is seen all day on 20 monitors strategically placed in high-traffic areas throughout the Las Vegas Convention Center, Las Vegas Hilton and Alexis Park Hotel.
<br><br>
Reinforce your marketing message with the audiovisual power that only TV advertising can deliver.  If your company doesn't have a commercial, CES' production company can produce an ad for you.
<br><br>
Also place your own TVs around the convention floor for CES-TV.  Call CES now for details!
<br><br>
